and iterative\nsolvers that, in many cases, have to be implemented on distributed-memory\narchitectures to be practical, a prerequisite. We showcase state-of-the-art\ntechniques in scientific computing to tackle these challenges.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Feb 2018 20:04:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-25"}
