reement with the RT simulation,\nour results suggests that constraining ionizing emissivity sensitive parameters\nfrom semi-numerical galaxy formation-reionization models are subject to photon\nnonconservation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Feb 2018 21:08:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-02"}
