on in $B_g$ value. For\n$\\chi=0$, we get the higher value for $B_g$ as the above mentioned predicted\nrange.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Feb 2018 18:37:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Dec 2018 15:42:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-31"}
